      "locked": false,
      "text": "🔥 Top LLDs that are VERY similar to Parking Lot\n1️⃣ Toll Booth System (Closest cousin)\n\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Toll Booth   |\n| ------------ | ------------ |\n| Vehicle      | Vehicle      |\n| Entry Gate   | Toll Entry   |\n| Exit Gate    | Toll Exit    |\n| Ticket       | Toll Ticket  |\n| Parking Spot | Lane         |\n| Invoice      | Toll Invoice |\n| Payment      | Payment      |\n\nWhat’s same?\n\nEntry → ticket issued\nExit → amount calculated\nPayment processed\n\nExtra learning\nFast payments (RFID / FASTag)\nNo parking duration, but distance / vehicle type\n\n\n2️⃣ Movie Ticket Booking System\nMapping\n\n| Parking Lot  | Movie Booking |\n| ------------ | ------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Seat          |\n| Floor        | Screen        |\n| Ticket       | Booking       |\n| Invoice      | Bill          |\n| Payment      | Payment       |\n\nWhat you learn\n\nSeat locking\nExpiry of booking\nStatus transitions (AVAILABLE → HELD → BOOKED)\nConcurrency handling\n\n\n3️⃣ Hotel Room Booking System\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Hotel       |\n| ------------ | ----------- |\n| Parking Spot | Room        |\n| Entry Time   | Check-in    |\n| Exit Time    | Check-out   |\n| Ticket       | Reservation |\n| Invoice      | Bill        |\n\nWhat’s new\n\nLong-lived bookings\nCancellation policies\nPartial payments\n\n\n\n4️⃣ Bike / Scooter Rental System\nVERY SIMILAR\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Rental System |\n| ------------ | ------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Dock          |\n| Ticket       | Rental        |\n| Entry Gate   | Start Ride    |\n| Exit Gate    | End Ride      |\n| Invoice      | Rental Bill   |\n\nExtra concepts\n\nUsage-based pricing\nDamages\nDeposits\n\n\n5️⃣ EV Charging Station System ⚡\nMapping\n\n| Parking Lot  | EV Charging      |\n| ------------ | ---------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Charging Slot    |\n| Ticket       | Charging Session |\n| Time         | Units consumed   |\n| Invoice      | Charging Bill    |\n\n\nWhat you learn\n\nMeter-based billing\nDynamic pricing\nSlot availability\n\n\n\n Coworking Space Desk Booking\n2️⃣ Gym Membership + Session Tracking\n3️⃣ Airport Lounge Access System\n4️⃣ Library Seat / Study Room Booking\n5️⃣ Warehouse Dock Allocation System\n6️⃣ Cloud VM / Resource Billing System\n7️⃣ Car Wash Management System\n8️⃣ Event Check-in System\n9️⃣ Doctor Appointment System\n🔟 Restaurant Table Booking",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🔥 Top LLDs that are VERY similar to Parking Lot\n1️⃣ Toll Booth System (Closest cousin)\n\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Toll Booth   |\n| ------------ | ------------ |\n| Vehicle      | Vehicle      |\n| Entry Gate   | Toll Entry   |\n| Exit Gate    | Toll Exit    |\n| Ticket       | Toll Ticket  |\n| Parking Spot | Lane         |\n| Invoice      | Toll Invoice |\n| Payment      | Payment      |\n\nWhat’s same?\n\nEntry → ticket issued\nExit → amount calculated\nPayment processed\n\nExtra learning\nFast payments (RFID / FASTag)\nNo parking duration, but distance / vehicle type\n\n\n2️⃣ Movie Ticket Booking System\nMapping\n\n| Parking Lot  | Movie Booking |\n| ------------ | ------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Seat          |\n| Floor        | Screen        |\n| Ticket       | Booking       |\n| Invoice      | Bill          |\n| Payment      | Payment       |\n\nWhat you learn\n\nSeat locking\nExpiry of booking\nStatus transitions (AVAILABLE → HELD → BOOKED)\nConcurrency handling\n\n\n3️⃣ Hotel Room Booking System\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Hotel       |\n| ------------ | ----------- |\n| Parking Spot | Room        |\n| Entry Time   | Check-in    |\n| Exit Time    | Check-out   |\n| Ticket       | Reservation |\n| Invoice      | Bill        |\n\nWhat’s new\n\nLong-lived bookings\nCancellation policies\nPartial payments\n\n\n\n4️⃣ Bike / Scooter Rental System\nVERY SIMILAR\nMapping:\n\n| Parking Lot  | Rental System |\n| ------------ | ------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Dock          |\n| Ticket       | Rental        |\n| Entry Gate   | Start Ride    |\n| Exit Gate    | End Ride      |\n| Invoice      | Rental Bill   |\n\nExtra concepts\n\nUsage-based pricing\nDamages\nDeposits\n\n\n5️⃣ EV Charging Station System ⚡\nMapping\n\n| Parking Lot  | EV Charging      |\n| ------------ | ---------------- |\n| Parking Spot | Charging Slot    |\n| Ticket       | Charging Session |\n| Time         | Units consumed   |\n| Invoice      | Charging Bill    |\n\n\nWhat you learn\n\nMeter-based billing\nDynamic pricing\nSlot availability\n\n\n\n Coworking Space Desk Booking\n2️⃣ Gym Membership + Session Tracking\n3️⃣ Airport Lounge Access System\n4️⃣ Library Seat / Study Room Booking\n5️⃣ Warehouse Dock Allocation System\n6️⃣ Cloud VM / Resource Billing System\n7️⃣ Car Wash Management System\n8️⃣ Event Check-in System\n9️⃣ Doctor Appointment System\n🔟 Restaurant Table Booking",
